m015">AKM-015</t:ref>a "Psalter"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm016">AKM-016</t:ref> "Miracles of Mary"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm017">AKM-017</t:ref> "Vita of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm018">AKM-018</t:ref> "Book of the Diciples"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm019">AKM-019</t:ref> "The Anaphora of Mary"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm020">AKM-020</t:ref> "The Anaphora of Mary"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm021">AKM-021</t:ref> "Collection of Mälkǝʿ-Poetry for Mary"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm022">AKM-022</t:ref> "collection of protective texts"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESakm023">AKM-023</t:ref> "Missal".</t:ab>
        
